description:
The brilliant Mayim Bialik (THE BIG BANG THEORY) is here for a brand new episode of Unqualified! First, Anna surprises Mayim with an armful of kittens before they talk about baking, the experience of being a woman in entertainment, and making friends outside of the industry. Then, Mayim tells us what it was like to be recognized as a child star in college and Anna reminds us of her Red Robin training video. Next, the group has a powerful conversation on co-parenting, divorce and raising children while in the spotlight. After that, Mayim shows off her Bronx accent and answers some dating deal breakers. Lastly, they call Alyssa, who found out that she is the "other woman", and Colleen, who feels like the third wheel in her group of girl friends. Tune in and enjoy!
